deal_title: Portronics Clamp M3 Adjustable Car Mobile Phone Holder Stand for Dashboard & Windshield, 360° Rotational, Strong Suction Cup, Compatible with 4 to 6 inch Devices(Black)
product_description: Perfect 2 in 1 Driving Partner: Secure your mobile while driving with Portronics Clamp M3 Car Mobile Holder. Whether you drive a car, truck, SUV, or taxi, this 2-in-1 holder attaches to your windshield or dashboard with its powerful gel suction cup. Bumpy Roads, No Worries: Don’t let bumps or turns affect your phone. The strong lock and gel suction cup keep your phone steady on rough roads. To reuse, simply rinse with warm water and wipe clean. Customized Viewing: Rotate your phone 360 degrees, pivot 180 degrees, and adjust height up to 40mm for the perfect angle. Enjoy hands-free navigation without blocking your view. Fits Your Phone Perfectly: Designed for 4-6 inches phones, the durable car mobile holder ensures compatibility with various devices. Plus, its smart design lets you connect charging cables conveniently. One Push Release: Install and release your phone in seconds with just one hand using the single-touch button. Keep your focus on the road as your phone remains stable and safe within reach. Built to Last: Made from scratch and shock-free ABS material, the Portronics Clamp M3 Car Windshield and Dashboard Mobile Holder promises durability and longevity. Your Navigation Companion: Ideal for drivers, this car phone holder is your perfect partner for using navigation maps. Stay on course while Clamp M3 keeps your phone steady and accessible.
